$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_amount

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_amount -  This method sets the amount of money associated with the cheque.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_amount(int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the amount of money to associate the cheque with
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the newly set amount or 0 if the amount has already been set

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/misc/cheque.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the amount of money associated with the cheque.
.EP

